data.description: $40,000 Price Adjustment! This Stunning Vanden Ranch home has 4 bedroom 3.5 bath and was built in 2016. As you enter the home, you are greeted with a bedroom featuring an ensuite bathroom, perfect for guests or as a second master suite. The main level also includes a full hall bath for added convenience. The heart of the home lies in the gourmet kitchen, complete with granite countertops, tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, built-in oven & microwave. The kitchen island with sink & dishwasher is perfect for meal prep, while the walk-in pantry provides ample storage space. Upstairs, you will find two additional guest bedrooms and the master suite. The master ensuite is spacious and features dual sinks, a vanity area, a soaking tub, and a stand-alone glass-enclosed shower. This home also boasts tall ceilings, recessed lighting, upstairs laundry & loft. Located in close proximity to freeways, schools, parks, restaurants, & shopping centers, this home offers both convenience and comfort. **SELLER willing to PAY towards Lender RATE BUY DOWN and/or closings costs. FHA assumable loan at 387k @ 4.125%** Some furniture can convey call for details *SEND US YOUR OFFERS*
